extendedInfo.description: Get the latest news, weather and Packers coverage from Northeast Wisconsin wherever you are with the NBC26 app. NBC26's app offers extensive coverage of the stories that matter most to you in Northeast Wisconsin. From NBC26 Today with Jennifer Dodd and Brian Niznansky, to Live at 10 p.m. with Stacy Engebretson, Cameron Moreland and Larry McCarren, our app provides you Wisconsin news throughout the day powered by nbc26.com. App features include: -The latest weather forecast from NBC 26 Chief Meteorologist Cameron Moreland and Brian Niznansky -Local and state politics and government, including updates from Madison - Information from Sports Director Larry McCarren on your favorite teams, including the Green Bay Packers, the Milwaukee Brewers, the Milwaukee Bucks, the Marquette Golden Eagles and the Wisconsin Badgers -News, sports and weather photos -Videos from our latest newscasts, as well as web exclusive videos -Station contests and promotions -School closings -A way to submit your story or photo to our station via iContribute Plus, you can easily share this content and connect to your friends and family using the Facebook feature on our app!

reviews.title: Works great, old news
reviews.comment: The app itself is great, and works well. The news content I find to be lacking and/or several days old. I get most of my news updates from other sites.
reviews.author: Tim Lorenz

reviews.title: Good images and navigation.
reviews.comment: Recommend app to those that are local. Works well on Samsung Galaxy.
reviews.author: Leroy Schlorf Jr

reviews.comment: Very nice! The weather feature is great!
reviews.author: A Google User
